CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1963, pg. 7 reads: "D.I.'s Go Formal - Pittsburgh's sleek D.I. Club gave its first strictly formal affair last Saturday night in Hotel Webster Hall, and drew an entrancingly gowned group of the feminine sex and their escorts. ...to say "thank you" to their guests. Shown here are D.I.'s chic in their floor length gowns.  Left to right; Mary Jean Eaton, Juanita Drake, Nellye Barron, Margaret Watson, Evelyn Christian and Gloria Grate. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five D.I. members, left to right; Nellye Barron, Mary Jean Eaton, Juanita Drake, shaking hands with man wearing patterned dinner jacket, Margaret Watson, and Evelyn Christian, standing in row in interior of Hotel Webster Hall for D.I. ball
